      "raw_text": "(By United Press Leased Wire)\nCINCINNATI, O., March 25.-FoI-\n\n\nlowing the failure of special CON-\nmittee of the United Mine Workers\nOf America to reach an agreement\n\n\nwith the mine operators in connec-\n\n\nton with a new wage scale it is\n\n\nexpected here today that the miners\n\n\nwill call an extra convention imme-\n\n\ndiately and vote to declare a strike.\n\n\nShould the strike be called, the min\n\n\ners would probably go out April 1,\nas the present contract between the\noperators and the miners will ex-\npire at that time."
